;
MSG_PV_WRITE_CANCEL
Write|Cancel
;
MSG_PV_OVERFLOW_INCREASE_BODY
Metadata overflow:\nneed %lu blocks, only %lu available\n(lo_cyl=%lu, %lu blks/cyl).\n\nIncrease reserved area to lo_cyl=%lu\nand write now?
;
MSG_PV_OVERFLOW_INCREASE_GADGETS
Increase & Write|Cancel
