WARNING: This will OVERWRITE block 0\non the disk with data from the backup file!\n\nRestoring an incorrect or mismatched backup\nWILL cause permanent data loss.\n\nEnsure the backup matches THIS disk.\n\nAre you absolutely sure?
;
MSG_RDB_EXT_RESTORE_WARN_BODY
WARNING: This will OVERWRITE multiple blocks\n(RDB, partitions, filesystems) on the disk!\n\nAn incorrect backup WILL destroy the disk layout.\nEnsure the backup matches THIS disk.\n\nAre you absolutely sure?
;
