MSG_MBR_SHARED_TITLE
Shared Disk
;
MSG_MBR_SHARED_BODY
Write an MBR at block 0 for shared disk access?\n(RDB will be placed at block 1 so the Amiga still finds it.)\n\nUseful for PiStorm, bridgeboards and other setups that\nneed to see a PC-style partition table on the same disk.
;
MSG_MBR_SHARED_GADGETS
Yes (MBR+RDB)|RDB only
;
